---
title: Steak au Poivre with Bacon Caesar Salad and Fries
description: On the menu tonight is a premium steakhouse classic that is sure to warm the soul! Juicy steak is adorned with an umami-filled pepper sauce and paired with a creamy kale Caesar and oven fries.
